title: Does federal food aid funds include the White House's reliance on Trump?
subtitle: More than 100 million food aid funds were distributed throughout the United States in 2020 in response to the Corona virus epidemic.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: In late September 2020, the United States Department of Agriculture distributed millions of federally funded aid funds, which included a letter from President Donald Trump documenting his administration for distribution.
